page.title: 09FAMILY HOLIDAY HIGH ERCALL
page.content: I went to Wales on my Holiday. We went to Cemes Bay and lots of other beaches. On the way, by car we had a breakfast picnic. When we got to our holiday house we unpacked then went to Cemes Bay. On Monday it was windy and rainy, So we went to a light house. On Thursday we went swimming. Then on Saturday we went home. On the way home we went to a Sea Zoo. Where we saw lobsters, crabs, starfish, and lots of different fish. I bought a badge which said, "I was bitten by Anglesey sea zoo".I had a nice time. By Jennifer Humphreys.
